    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hmm, this is a good catch. It seems like we removed a condition erroneously, which causes the library  to think insights is always enabled, even while it's not done by the user. See https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/commit/9cac5a3aa4af616ec7913c17ed7388134c5e7f0a#diff-3eeb23719bab17ca03a8f33b4d1df9c5L15-L17 (cc @tkrugg)\r\n\r\nFor now you can simply  ignore that error message, since it won't impact your search, but this is definitely a bug",
